data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: What we can see is that two women are walking in the street. One of them is pushing a pram, and the other one has a water bottle in one of her hands. There are many other pedestrians in the street as well. They are all heading in the same direction. There is probably some sort of public assembly they are going to attend.
